  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/50px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/75px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/100px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Theo Frey</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/50px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/75px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/100px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Theo Frey</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> His relationship with Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a> is not specified, though he is probably a grandson.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Theo_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Theo_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser Theo attends the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand%27s_tourney\" title=\"Hand&#39;s tourney\">Hand's tourney</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> with six of his kin—Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Hosteen_Frey\" title=\"Hosteen Frey\">Hosteen</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Danwell_Frey\" title=\"Danwell Frey\">Danwell</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jared_Frey\" title=\"Jared Frey\">Jared</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Emmon_Frey\" title=\"Emmon Frey\">Emmon</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Perwyn_Frey\" title=\"Perwyn Frey\">Perwyn</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Martyn_Rivers\" title=\"Martyn Rivers\">Martyn Rivers</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Theo_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_29\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 29\">Chapter 29</a>, Sansa II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403134556\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.078 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.272 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 773/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10502/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 